name: Latios
Attack1Text: Flip a coin. If heads, search your deck for a basic Energy card and attach it to 1 of your Pokemon. Shuffle your deck afterward.

name: Linoone
Attack1Text: Search your deck for up to 2 cards and put them into your hand. Shuffle your deck afterward.
Attack2Text: Flip a coin until you get tails. This attack does 40 damage times the number of heads.

name: Magneton
Attack2Text: Flip 3 coins. This attack does 20 damage plus 20 more damage for each heads.

name: Zigzagoon
Attack1Text: Flip 3 coins. This attack does 10 damage times the number of heads.
